title: Establishes environmental standards and protections in the insurance business, and provides incentives and tax credits for offering green insurance
summary: Establishes environmental standards and protections in the insurance business, and provides incentives and tax credits for offering green insurance.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, the workers' compensation law and the tax law, in relation to establishing environmental standards and protections in the insurance business, and providing incentives and tax credits for offering green insurance
